OL,5, Asking adults to wear a mask if they   
OL,6, have a respiratory infection and need  
OL,7, to go out is sensible, ministers say.  
OL,9,FTransport Secretary Mark Harper said he
OL,10,Ffully supported the guidance, issued by
OL,11,Fthe UK Health Security Agency (UKHSA). 
OL,13,FThe advice, in place for months in     
OL,14,FEngland, was reiterated by the UKHSA as
OL,15,Fschools and workplaces return after the
OL,16,FChristmas break.                       
OL,18,FIt comes amid mounting pressure on the 
OL,19,FNHS, partly driven by high rates of    
OL,20,FCovid and flu.                         
